SARS-CoV-2 ayaa la sheegay inuu xasaasi u yahay waxyaabaha soo socda ee si wax ku ool ah u joojin kara fayraska: UV iyo 30 daqiiqo heerkulka 56 °C; ether, 75% ethanol, chlorine, acid plasticized, chloroform iyo saliidaha kale ee dufanka, laakiin chlorhexidine ma laha awooddan.
