Sababtoo ah khibrad la'aanta coronavirus-ka cusub, dhakhaatiirtu waxay inta badan daryeelayaan daryeelka taageerada ee bukaannada COVID-19, iyagoo isku dayaya inay adeegsadaan daaweyn kala duwan oo loo adeegsaday ama lagu soo jeediyay daaweynta cudurrada hore ee coronavirus-ka, oo ay ku jiraan SARS-CoV iyo MERS-CoV iyo cudurrada kale ee fayraska (Jadwalka 2).
Daaweynta waxaa ka mid ah daaweynta maskaxda iyo suurtagalka ah ee daawooyinka antiviral, kahortagga nidaamka difaaca, steroids, plasma ee bukaanada soo kabsaday, daawo Shiine ah iyo taageero nafsaani ah.
