Si kastaba ha noqotee, waxaa lagula talinayaa in si taxaddar leh loo isticmaalo daaweynta kortikosteroids-ka ee qiyaasta hooseysa illaa dhexdhexaadka ah ee loogu talagalay daaweynta bukaannada COVID-19 ee halista ah.
