Ugu dambeyntii, SARS-CoV-2 waxaa lagu ogaan karaa shaybaarka qallalan sida HCoVs kale.
Ma cadda in gudbinta afka-afka ee SARS-CoV-2 ay ka ciyaareyso door muhiim ah sida SARS-CoV, ugu yaraan xaaladaha qaarkood.
Waxaa xiiso leh in la arko haddii SARS-CoV-2 uu yahay mid xilliyeed sida kiisaska coronavirus-ka aadanaha ee faafitaanka ballaaran.
Si kastaba ha noqotee, astaamaha SARS-CoV-2 oo ay ku jiraan gudbinta, cudur-qaadista iyo sii-socoshada joogtada ah ka dib markii laga gudbiyo aadanaha ayaa saameyn ku yeelan doona masiirka ugu dambeeya ee faafitaanka sii socda ee COVID-19.
Afarta HCoVs waxay si fiican ula qabsadeen dadka, iyadoo ay jiraan faafitaan ballaaran oo sababa calaamado fudud.
Marka laga eego dhinaca kale, waxaa laga yaabaa inay sax tahay in la yiraahdo aadanuhu si fiican ayey ula qabsadeen afarta HCoVs.
Taasi waa, labaduba waxay noqon karaan kuwo ka badbaaday cudurrada faafa ee HCoV-ga hore.
Human CoVs oo keena cudurrada daran ee dadka iyo dadka qaba cudurrada daran ee Human CoVs ayaa laga saaray daraasadda.
Si taas loo gaaro, HCoVs waa inay ku badsadaan bini'aadamka si ay u oggolaadaan isku-darka is-beddelka is-beddelka ee ka hortagaya arrimaha xaddidan ee martida.
Marka, sida uu SARS-CoV-2 u sii socdo, iyo sida ay dad badani u qaadaan cudurka, fayrasku wuxuu leeyahay fursad weyn oo uu ku habboonaado bini'aadamka.
Haddii fayraska uu si fiican isu beddelay, waxaa adag in laga hortago gudbinta iyada oo loo marayo karantiil ama habab kale oo xakamaynta cudurka.
Muddo sanado ah, afar coronavirus ayaa ku faafay dadweynaha, waxayna sababeen in dadka qaba nidaamka difaaca jirka ee aan si fiican u shaqeynin ay ku dhacaan cudurro caadi ah.
Fayrasyadaasi uma baahna kayd xayawaan.
Dhinaca kale, fayrasyada SARS-CoV iyo MERS-CoV ee cudurrada sare leh si fiican uma la qabsan bini'aadamka, isgaarsiintoodana kuma sii socon karto bini'aadamka.
Waxay u baahan yihiin inay ku noolaadaan oo ay ku tarmaan kaydka xayawaanka, inta badan hal ama in ka badan oo martida dhexdhexaadka ah iyo kuwa tarjumaya, iyagoo raadinaya fursad ay ugu gudbiyaan dadka xasaasiga ah.
