Daraasado dhowr ah oo cusub oo ku saleysan taxanaha metagenomic ayaa muujinaya in koox ka mid ah naasleyda yaryar ee halista ku jira ee loo yaqaan 'pangolin' (Manis javanica) ay sidoo kale noqon karaan asalka awoowayaasha SARS-CoV-2 ee la xiriira beta-CoV.
