Dusha sare waxaa lagu nadiifin karaa dhowr xal (hal daqiiqo oo nadiifin ah oo lagu soo bandhigo dusha sare ee birta birta ah), oo ay ku jiraan 62-71% ethanol, 50-100% isopropanol, 0.1% sodium hypochlorite, 0.5% hydrogen peroxide iyo 0.2-7.5% iodine powidone.
