Sida ku xusan talooyinka CDC, haddii qof laga shakiyo inuu qaba COVID ama uu ku jiro goob sida xafiis ama xarun caafimaad, dhammaan goobaha sida xafiisyada, adeegyada caafimaadka, goobaha la wadaago, qalabka elektarooniga ah ee la wadaago sida kiniiniyada, shaashadaha taabashada, kumbuyuutarrada, kontaroolada fog iyo gawaarida ATM ee ay isticmaalaan bukaanku waa in la nadiifiyaa.
Ururada caafimaadka ayaa dadka kula talinaya in ay gacmaha ama gacmaha ku daboolaan afka iyo sanka marka ay qufacayaan ama qufacayaan, isla markaana ay si degdeg ah u tuuraan dharka waraaqaha ah.
Maaskaro qalliin ayaa lagula talinayaa dadka laga yaabo inay cudurka qabaan, maadaama maaskaro ay yareyn karto mugga iyo masaafada ay ka baxdo dhibcaha neefsashada marka la hadlayo, qufacayo iyo qufacayo.
Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka ayaa soo saaray tilmaamo ku saabsan goorta iyo sida loo isticmaalo maaskaro.
Stephen Griffin, oo ah cilmi-nafsiga cudurka ee Jaamacadda Leeds, ayaa sheegay in "xidhashada maaskaro ay yareyn karto rabitaanka dadka inay taabtaan wajiga, oo ah sababta ugu weyn ee loo gudbiyo cudurka, iyagoo gacmaha taagan". Maaskaro ayaa sidoo kale lagula talinayaa dadka daryeela kiisaska laga shakiyo.
Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka ayaa ku taliyey dadka caafimaadka qaba inay isticmaalaan maaskaro kaliya marka ay khatar sare ku jiraan, tusaale ahaan daryeelka dadka qaba COVID-19, inkasta oo ay xaqiijisay in maaskaro ay ka caawin karto dadka inaysan taaban wejiga.
Dalal badan ayaa bilaabay inay dadka ku dhiirrigeliyaan isticmaalka maaskaro wajiga.
