Dadka waxaa la siiyaa daryeel taageero ah oo ay ka mid noqon karaan daaweynta dareeraha, oksijiinta dheeriga ah iyo taageerada xubnaha kale ee muhiimka ah.
CDC waxay ku talineysaa dadka laga shakisan yahay inay yihiin kuwa qaada cudurka inay isticmaalaan maaskaro waji oo fudud.
Isticmaalka oksijiinta ee ka baxsan jirka (ECMO) ayaa loo isticmaalay in lagu daaweeyo neefsashada oo aan la daaweyn karin, laakiin faa'iidooyinka ayaa wali la baarayaa.
Xakamaynta caafimaadka shakhsiga ah iyo hab nololeed caafimaad leh iyo cunto ayaa lagu talinayaa in la hagaajiyo nidaamka difaaca.
Daawooyinka taageerada ayaa laga yaabaa inay waxtar u yeeshaan dadka qaba calaamadaha fudud iyo marxaladaha hore ee caabuqa. Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO) iyo Guddiga Caafimaadka Qaranka ee Shiinaha (Chinese National Health Commission) ayaa soo saaray talooyin ku saabsan daryeelka dadka isbitaalada la dhigay sababo la xiriira COVID-19.
Xirfadlayaasha daryeelka degdegga ah iyo kuwa cudurka sanbabada ee Mareykanka ayaa ku soo ururiyay talooyinka daaweynta hay'adaha kala duwan ilaha bilaashka ah ee IBCC.
Ilaa Abriil 2020, ma jiro daaweyn gaar ah oo loogu talagalay COVID-19.
Qaar ka mid ah xirfadlayaasha caafimaadka ayaa doorbidaya daaweynta bilowga ah ee paracetamol si loo yareeyo calaamadaha marka loo eego ibuprofen.
Si loo yareeyo khatarta qaadashada fayraska, taxaddar ayaa loo baahan yahay, gaar ahaan deegaanka daaweynta, halkaas oo walxaha la isku xidho ay soo saari karaan inta lagu jiro geedi socodka, sida tuubooyinka iyo isticmaalka qalabka neefsashada gacanta.
Xirfadlayaasha daryeelka caafimaadka ee daryeela dadka qaba COVID-19, CDC waxay ku talineysaa in marka lagu daro isticmaalka taxaddarrada caadiga ah, taxaddarka xiriirka iyo xakamaynta cudurrada hawada laga qaado, in qofka lagu meeleeyo qolka karantiil ee cudurrada hawada laga qaado (AIIR). CDC waxay sharaxeysaa habraacyada isticmaalka qalabka ilaalinta shakhsiga (PPE) inta lagu jiro masiibada.
Qalabka lagu taliyey waxaa ka mid ah: PPE, nidaamka neefsashada ama wajiga, ilaalinta indhaha iyo gacmo gashiyada caafimaadka. Haddii la heli karo, waxaa la doorbidayaa mashiinada neefsashada (halkii ay ka ahaan lahayd wajiga).
Filter-ka N95 ee neefsashada ayaa loo oggolaaday goobaha warshadaha, laakiin FDA waxay oggolaatay isticmaalka waji-xidhka oo keliya xaaladaha loo oggolaaday isticmaalka degdegga ah (EUA).
Waxaa loogu talagalay in lagu ilaaliyo walxaha hawada ku dhex jira sida boodhka, laakiin waxtarkooda ma ahan mid la xaqiijiyay oo ka dhan ah walxaha bayoolojiga ee loogu talagalay isticmaalka aan ku xusan sumadda.
CDC waxay ku talineysaa isticmaalka ilaalinta wajiga, ama sida ugu dambeysa, maaskaro guriga lagu xirto marka maaskaro aan la heli karin.
Inta badan kiisaska COVID-19 ma ahan kuwo aad u daran oo u baahan neefsashada farsamada ama wax la mid ah, laakiin boqolkiiba dadka qaba cudurka ayaa u baahan.
Nooca gargaarka neefsashada ee ay u baahan yihiin bukaannada qaba cudurka neefsashada ee COVID-19 ayaa hadda lagu daraasayaa dadka isbitaalka ku jira, waxaana caddeyn lagu muujiyay in isticmaalka tuubbo cadaadis sare leh ama cadaadis hawada oo badh ahaan wanaagsan laga hortagi karo in la geeyo neefsashada.
Lama oga in labada nooc ay faa'iido isku mid ah u leeyihiin dadka qaba cudurka daran.
Dhakhaatiirta qaarkood waxay doorbidaan in la sii wado hawo-qaadista farsamada ee weerarka ah marka la gaaro, maadaama ay xaddideyso kala-baxa aerosol marka la barbar dhigo daaweynta oksijiinta sanka ee kor u kaca. Kiisaska degdegga ah ayaa ugu badan dadka da'doodu ka weyn tahay 60 sano, gaar ahaan dadka ka weyn 80 sano.
Wadamada horumaray badankood ma haystaan isbitaal ku filan, taas oo xaddideysa awoodda nidaamka caafimaadka ee wax ka qabashada kororka degdegga ah ee COVID-19 ee aadka ugu baahan isbitaal degenaansho.
Daraasad lagu sameeyay Shiinaha ayaa muujisay in 5% ay ku jiraan qeybaha daryeelka degdegga ah, 2.3% waxay u baahan yihiin caawimaad neefsashada farsamada, 1.4% waxay dhinteen.
Shiinaha, qiyaastii 30% dadka isbitaalka la dhigay COVID-19 ayaa loo wareejiyay ICU.
Hawo-qaadista farsamada ayaa sii murugsan marka cudurka neefsashada oo daran (ARDS) uu ku sii socdo COVID-19 iyo bixinta oksijiinta ayaa sii adkaaneysa.
Hawo-mareenada, oo ay ku jiraan hababka xakamaynta cadaadiska iyo PEEP-ga oo la kordhiyay, ayaa loo isticmaalaa in lagu kordhiyo gudbinta oksijiinta isla markaana la yareeyo halista dhaawaca sanbabada ee la xiriira nidaamka neefsashada iyo pneumothorax.
Qalabka kor u kaca ee PEEP waxaa laga yaabaa in aan la helin hawo-qaboojiyayaasha duugga ah.
Cilmi baaris ku saabsan daaweynta suurtagalka ah ayaa bilaabatay Janaayo 2020, waxaana jira dhowr daawooyin antiviral ah oo lagu arkay daraasadaha caafimaad.
Remdesivir ayaa ah tii ugu waxtarka badneyd ilaa hadda.
Inkastoo ay dhici karto in 2021 la soo saaro daawo cusub, daawooyin badan oo tijaabo ah ayaa loo adeegsaday isticmaal kale ama horay loo xaqiijiyay tijaabooyin horumarsan.
Daawooyinka ka hortaga fayraska waxaa laga yaabaa in lagu tijaabiyo dadka qaba cudurrada daran.
Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka ayaa ku taliyey in iskaa wax u qabso ay ka qayb galaan tijaabooyinka lagu ogaanayo waxtarka iyo ka-hortagga daawooyinka suurtagalka ah. Hay'adda Cuntada iyo Dawooyinka ee Mareykanka ayaa si ku meelgaar ah u oggolaatay isticmaalka plasma-ka dadka soo kabsaday (convalescent plasma) sida daaweyn tijaabo ah oo loogu talagalay xaaladaha nolosha ee halista weyn ama tooska ah.
Ma ahan mid la sameeyey daraasado caafimaad oo loo baahan yahay si loo muujiyo ka-hortagga iyo waxtarka cudurka.
